    {
      Id = "Storyteller_0177"
      InheritFrom = "BaseNarrative"
      DisplayName = "{#Emph}From nothingness sprang all creation, light, and darkness, and the world itself; yet all that nothingness remains, carefully tucked away where none can find it, save for those invited in."
